[ORG Finmeccanica] is an [MISC Italian] state - owned holding company with interests in the mechanical engineering industry . 
[ORG Bailey Controls] , based in [LOC Wickliffe] , [LOC Ohio] , makes computerized industrial controls systems . 
It employs 2,700 people and has annual revenue of about $ 370 million . 
The federal government suspended sales of [LOC U.S.] savings bonds because [ORG Congress] has n't lifted the ceiling on government debt . 
Until [ORG Congress] acts , the government has n't any authority to issue new debt obligations of any kind , the [ORG Treasury] said . 
The government 's borrowing authority dropped at midnight Tuesday to $ 2.80 trillion from $ 2.87 trillion . 
Legislation to lift the debt ceiling is ensnarled in the fight over cutting capital - gains taxes . 
The [LOC House] has voted to raise the ceiling to $ 3.1 trillion , but the [ORG Senate] is n't expected to act until next week at the earliest . 
The [ORG Treasury] said the [LOC U.S.] will default on Nov. 9 if [ORG Congress] does n't act by then . 
