[PER Dmitry Medvedev] examined Topol-M intercontinental ballistic missiles concealed by the military in a dense pine forest and spoke to officers at the base in teikovo . 
[PER Dmitry Medvedev] was impressed by the weapons and the level of training . 
[PER Dmitry Medvedev] also stated that it is good that the military is getting new missiles like the Topol-M . 
