[PER Dmitry Medvedev] was sworn in on May 7 , 2008 as the [LOC Russian Federation] 's President and has so far portrayed an image of a liberal and avoided the harsh anti-western rhetoric of [PER Vladimir Putin] . 
[PER Vladimir Putin] was [PER Dmitry Medvedev] 's predecessor and mentor . 
Most observers expect [PER Dmitry Medvedev] to continue the policies of [PER Vladimir Putin] , such as an assertive posture on the international scene and vow to strengthen the military . 
