20080710 director of the [ORG London] -based [ORG International Institute for Strategic Studies] 's non-proliferation program and former [ORG US State Department] official [PER Mark Fitzpatrick] stated that an [MISC Iranian] photograph showing a cluster of missile launches from a desert range was altered to add a 4th missile . 
