This included a funeral Director who had transported the body of [PER Efrain Torres] to a cemetery in the city of [LOC Poza Rica] in May . 
[PER Torres] was an assassinated leader of the zetas . 
The body later was stolen from its crypt . 
Another victim of the violence in [LOC Veracruz] cannot yet be tallied among the dead . 
Business owner [PER Roberto moguel] [PER Martinez] was kidnapped by armed men on June 6 , 2007 after being released from a hospital . 
[PER Martinez] had been recovering from wounds suffered in a May 31 , 2007 attack . 
[PER Martinez] 's mother wrestled briefly with [PER Martinez] 's armed kidnappers on a street in the center of the city according to the [LOC Veracruz] newspaper notiver . 
[PER Martinez] has not been seen since . 
On June 7 , 2007 there were three grenade attacks on two police stations and an army barracks in the southern state of [LOC Guerrero] . 
Authorities said seven people were killed in apparent drug-related attacks there . 
The websites of [LOC Mexico City] newspapers on June 8 , 2007 reported as many as 20 people had been gunned down nationwide in drug-related violence the previous 24 hours . 
