[PER Calderon] said that this is a shared problem between the [LOC United States] and [LOC Mexico] . 
The principal cause is the use of drugs . 
And the [LOC U.S.] is the prime consumer in the world . 
[PER Calderon] has sent the army to numerous [MISC Mexican] states to fill in for over-matched and corrupt local police . 
