[ORG Xinhua News Agency] , [LOC Nanjing] , April 23rd , by reporter [PER Futian Yang] 
[ORG Zijin Mountain Observatory] of the [LOC China Academy] [ORG Of Sciences] announced today that a nation - wide observation network for the collision of Shoemaker - [ORG Levy] 9 [ORG Comet] with [LOC Jupiter] had been built in [LOC China] and a large - scale astronomical observation plan had been formulated as well . 
According to experts , [LOC Jupiter] , which orbits the [ORG Sun] like the [LOC Earth] , is the largest planet in the solar system . 
This incident of observing of the comet colliding with [LOC Jupiter] possesses extremely important significance in researching and forecasting comets colliding with [LOC Earth] . 
The [MISC Chinese] astronomy arena also places great importance on this phenomenon of the comet colliding with [LOC Jupiter] and will closely focus attention on its development and changes . 
In the past few days , under the support of the [MISC Chinese] [ORG Academy of Sciences] and the [ORG National Natural Science Foundation] , a seminar on the plan to monitor comet Shoemaker - [PER Levy] 9 colliding with [LOC Jupiter] convened in [LOC Nanjing] and more than forty astronomers from all over the country attended . 
Experts think that this rare and important astronomical phenomenon requires continuous global observation , and that [LOC China] is located at an important longitudinal position between [LOC Japan] and [LOC Europe] , so , [LOC China] 's observational material from is an indispensable and irreplaceable component in the international joint observation . 
At that time , [LOC China] will put all advanced astronomical equipment to use to carry out observation , including 2.16 - meter reflecting telescopes , 1.26 - meter infrared telescopes and radio telescopes . 
25 - meter telescopes in the decimeter and centimeter wave bands , 10 - meter wave band telescopes and advanced optical telescope terminal equipment will also be used . 
[LOC Nanjing Zijin Mountain Observatory] has more than forty years of experience in the observation and research of comets and asteroids , and its planet research office is the only scientific research organization in [LOC China] conducting long term research on comets and asteroids , and since 1988 also started researching the issues of the solar system 's celestial bodies colliding . 
This station 's planet experts also attended many international scientific seminars on the dangers of comets and asteroids colliding with [LOC Earth] . 
