[ORG Xinhua News Agency] , [LOC Moscow] , August 31 , by reporter [PER Rong Xie] 
[LOC Russia] 's last group of personnel that should withdraw of the [LOC Northwest] military troop stationed in the three countries of the [LOC Baltic Sea] completely withdrew from [LOC Latvia] on the 31st . 
Until now , [LOC Russia] has completed the troop withdrawal work from the three countries of [LOC Baltic Sea] . 
It is reported by news media here that on the 31st , the personnel of the [MISC Russian] [ORG Northwest] troop headquarters turned over military installations to the local government , submitted a report to [MISC Latvian] president [PER Ulmanis] regarding the completion of troop withdrawal , and then withdrew from [LOC Riga] to [LOC Moscow] by plane . 
[MISC Russian] troops stationed in [LOC Lithuania] already withdrew back home before August 31st of 1993 , and troops stationed in [LOC Estonia] completed troop withdrawal work on the 29th of this month . 
According to agreements reached by [LOC Russia] with the governments of [LOC Latvia] and [LOC Estonia] , currently there are still a few hundred [MISC Russian] military experts remaining in the early warning radar stations of the [MISC Latvian] and [MISC Russian] naval education centers in [LOC Estonia] . 
The [MISC Russian] Northwest troop clusters are former [MISC Soviet] troops stationed in the above three countries , with headquarters set in the [MISC Latvian] Republic . 
The total original military strength was more than 116,000 people , within which most , more than 50,000 people , were stationed in [LOC Latvia] ; more than 35,000 people in [LOC Lithuania] , and more than 30,000 people in [LOC Estonia] . 
After the disintegration of the former [LOC Soviet Union] , these troop clusters were transferred to [MISC Russian] ownership . 
It is reported that the [MISC Russian] troops that withdrew from the three [LOC Baltic Sea] countries will be stationed respectively in the [MISC Russian] state of [LOC Jalininggele] , the state of [LOC Simolingsike] and [LOC Yelinia] city which is 300 kilometers away from [LOC Moscow] . 
( End ) 
